Description:
GRAND FAMILY LIVING
Grand family living in The Hunt Club.
A stunning spacious 5 bedroom home, beautifully presented and offering an abundance of space and entertaining options
Exceptional frontage with ample parking and curved driveway lined with established gardens provides privacy and appeal.
3 Superb living areas beautifully filled with natural light, including formal living and dining, separate family and central dining / pool room featuring the log fire to keep you warm and cosy throughout winter.
In addition the extensive undercover outdoor area can comfortably accomodate all your entertaining needs.
Be surrounded by family in your hostess kitchen appointed with quality granite bench tops, island bench with breakfast bar, stainless gas cook top, wall oven and dishwasher.
The master bedroom positioned at the at the front of the home, provides privacy and space fitted with walk-in robe and generous ensuite
4 additional bedrooms are all complete with built -in robes The 5th bedroom can also utilised as a study.
Other essential features include central heating and cooling, Tasmania Oak hardwood floors, feature floor tiling, generous laundry with storage and bench space, double garage with rear access roller door, large block 767m2(approx) low maintenance gardens and much much more.
Located within easy access of Cranbourne East primary and Secondary College, Early learning centre, Hunt Club Village Shopping Centre, walking tracks and parks. Ideally located close to public transport and links to major arterials.
This impressive home will tick all the boxes, call to arrange your inspection.
Internal area
245m²

Description:
FAMILY FRIENDLY - CASCADES ON CLYDE
CRANBOURNE EAST - CASCADES ON CLYDE - Set in the family-friendly estate of Cascades on Clyde this home would suit a young family or first home buyer. Within walking distance to parklands, 2 shopping precincts, medical facilities, sporting facilities and Wilandra Rise Primary School.
Offering 4 bedrooms, master with full ensuite and walk-in robe. Light and bright living areas and functional floor plan for day to day living.
Central kitchen with island benchtop and modern appliances will be the hub of this home, cooking for the family will be a delight and convenient.
Features include:
-Ducted heating
-Split system
-Play equipment and cubby house for the kids to enjoy
-Garden shed
-Double remote garage with internal access
-Dishwasher and stainless steel appliances
Surrounded by top-end properties and is within walking distance to picturesque wetlands, this home boasts convenience. Other estate features include Class-A recycled water ensuring lush gardens year-round, over 14 hectares of parkland and public open space, public BBQ facilities, playgrounds and walking tracks.
Those who are business savvy will appreciate this Telstra smart community positioned within a short drive to all amenities located in the townships of Berwick, Clyde and Cranbourne. Minutes away from freeway access en route to the Melbourne CBD, the popular Clyde Primary School, Casey Fields football ground/Casey Race aquatic centre and the Town Centre. Not to mention just minutes away from the Selandra Rise and Hunt Club village shopping centres.
BOOK AN INSPECTION TODAY, IT MAY BE GONE TOMORROW - PHOTO ID REQUIRED AT OPEN FOR INSPECTIONS!

Description:
Glamourous Style in Cascades on Clyde
Brilliantly designed four bedroom home on 622m2 is minutes to Cascades on Clyde wetlands, parklands and Selandra Rise shopping precinct. Offering enduring appeal through its subtle flair, numerous features and zoned layout. Combined with three living spaces, outdoor entertaining and a spacious sunlit backyard, the home caters marvellously for every family, every lifestyle.
Boasting a light and bright neutral interior, the tiled entrance hall opens upon the formal lounge seamlessly flowing through to the entertainer's kitchen. Here the hub of the home with S/S appliances and breakfast bench overlooks the meals, living room and alfresco - creating superb indoor / outdoor amenities for relaxing with family and friends. Additionally, the separate rumpus lends itself to a fun filled kid's zone.
Complemented by a further three sizeable bedrooms with BIRs, the master at the front of the home boasts dual sink ensuite and fitted WIR. Stylish family bathroom with bath, shower and separate powder room, good sized laundry and DLUG with internal access. Other notable features include ducted heating, evaporative cooling, ample storage and low maintenance garden.
Enjoying a most family friendly location being close to Cranbourne East PS, Secondary College, and an easy stroll only minutes to public transport.
*Contact agent to arrange a private inspection

Description:
Modern Appeal & Perfect Location
Private Inspection by Appointment Only!!
This gorgeous modern home will tick all the boxes for first home buyers and investors alike.
Situated perfectly in the Mayfield Estate Cranbourne East, this beautiful home will appeal to those who enjoy all things modern and the convenience of low maintenance.
Comprising of 3 beautifully light filled bedrooms, complete with built-in robes. In addition the master bedroom located at the front of the home provides privacy and space, with walk-in robe and ensuite.
The generous main bathroom will accomodate a growing family and offers great storage, separate toilet and that modern touch.
The open plan living and dining merge perfectly with the kitchen to make entertaining effortless. The kitchen is adequately equipped with stainless appliances, gas cook top, dishwasher, stone benches and window splash back will allow you to serve in style. The adjoining alfresco and rear garden makes for a superb retreat.
Beautifully styled modern home in neutral tones, additional features include:
- gorgeous blonde tone floating floors
- ducted heating, split system cooling
- garage internal access, garage rear access
- side gate, low maintenance gardens
All within a short distance to local amenities and shopping, sporting facilities and public transport. And directly across from the proposed football /netball sports pavilion due to be completed in 2021.
Ready to move in! a must see, call to arrange an inspection.

Description:
SOLD!
CRANBOURNE EAST: If you have been searching for the perfect property to break into the market, downsize into or add to your property portfolio without having to endure a lengthy building process then I suggest you snap up this fine opportunity.
This property offers a free flowing floor plan sure to be appreciated by all. Positioned on a low maintenance allotment, the property offers 4 spacious robed bedroom all with BIR's and space heaters. The master bedroom has a full ensuite, walk through robes & a balcony, there is one bedroom downstairs that is great for an office, visitors or anyone that struggles with stairs, along with a powder room. The hostess kitchen is complete with great bench and cupboard space, stone bench tops, 600mm cook top, range hood & dishwasher, all this and a whole lot more adjoining the open and bright meals & family room.
Extra internal extras and inclusions are 2nd living area/ landing upstairs, S/S air con, a great mix of quality tiles, carpet and floorboards & neutral paint tones throughout.
Outside your will be greeted by a modern facade, basic landscaping, a remote SLUG plus a roomy, carefree back yard with colour bond fencing, shedding and room to construct a pergola area (S.T.C.A.).
Cranbourne East is located on the outskirts of Cranbourne Central. The area offers Cranbourne East Primary and Cranbourne East Secondary College as well as Cranbourne Secondary College and is surrounded by multiple Shopping Centres. Also located nearby is the newly constructed Casey Fields football ground, Casey Race Recreation & Aquatic Centre, and Casey Library.
Our floor plans are for representational purposes only and should be used as such. We accept no liability for the accuracy or details contained in our floor plans.

Description:
A Fantastic First Home, So Close To Everything
In the popular Brindalee Estate, Cranbourne East, so close to absolutely everything, this well presented 3 bedroom home on a 450m2 corner block makes a fantastic first home and also offers side street access, great for a boat, a caravan and off street parking.
The home features all good size rooms, with a large formal lounge, a really good size kitchen for the chefs with 900mm gas hotplates and an electric wall oven, and plenty of bench space that overlooks the spacious dining area with timber floating floors and opens out onto the paved patio and the big backyard that extends all the way around the home.
Other extras include 3 good size bedrooms each with robes and the master offers a full ensuite, there is ducted heating throughout, a double garage and side access for a tradie with a trailer or someone with a caravan or boat.
All of this is only 2 minutes walk to Aldi, Woolworths, Dan Murphys, cafes, take away food, parks, lakes, bus stop, medical centre, Child Care, and 15 minutes walk to both Primary and Secondary Schools, the train station and the Settlement Hotel.
A fantastic first home opportunity, come take a look.
